data.description: This spacious fully renovated historic bungalow boasts Tower Of America views, open floor plan, restored wood flooring throughout, modern touches throughout, large primary suite with walk in closet, bathroom with soaking tub and walk in shower. Located in one of the top neighborhoods of San Antonio (Lavaca), this home has generous entertaining space with lots of natural lighting.
